longInfo:
Passport required.
- Passports and other documents accepted for entry issued to
  nationals of Iceland must be valid for the period of
  intended stay. 

VISA NOT REQUIRED.

Minors:
- WARNING! In accordance with European Union (EU) Legislation,
  all minors who are nationals of Iceland will be expected to
  hold their own passport or National ID Card (where
  applicable) when departing from Bulgaria, Croatia, Cyprus,
  Romania or a Schengen Member State . 
- All minors who are nationals of Iceland are expected to hold
  their own travel document.
Additional Information:
- Nationals of Iceland staying in Switzerland for more than 3
  months must apply for a residence permit.
- Geneva airport (GVA) is located by convention in
  Switzerland
